title: Help refresh Hillsboro Village dragon mural Oct. 31 October 23, 2015 (Vanderbilt University)
text: ( Source : Vanderbilt University ) Oct. 23, 2015 , 2:36 PM The dragon mural at 1801 21st Ave. S. in Hillsboro Village . Hillsboro Village neighbors, merchants and business owners are collaborating on a refresh of the 20-year-old dragon mural
